{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Cholera was reported in Haiti"},{"time":2000,"text":"for the first time in over 50 years"},{"time":4000,"text":"last October."},{"time":6000,"text":"There was no way to predict"},{"time":8000,"text":"how far it would spread through water supplies"},{"time":11000,"text":"and how bad the situation would get."},{"time":14000,"text":"And not knowing where help was needed"},{"time":16000,"text":"always ensured that help was in short supply"},{"time":19000,"text":"in the areas that needed it most."}]},{"cues":[{"time":22000,"text":"We've gotten good at predicting and preparing for storms"},{"time":25000,"text":"before they take innocent lives"},{"time":27000,"text":"and cause irreversible damage,"},{"time":29000,"text":"but we still can't do that with water,"},{"time":31000,"text":"and here's why."},{"time":33000,"text":"Right now, if you want to test water in the field,"},{"time":35000,"text":"you need a trained technician,"},{"time":37000,"text":"expensive equipment like this,"},{"time":39000,"text":"and you have to wait about a day"},{"time":41000,"text":"for chemical reactions to take place and provide results."},{"time":44000,"text":"It's too slow"},{"time":46000,"text":"to get a picture of conditions on the ground"},{"time":48000,"text":"before they change,"},{"time":50000,"text":"too expensive to implement"},{"time":52000,"text":"in all the places that require testing."},{"time":54000,"text":"And it ignores the fact that, in the meanwhile,"},{"time":56000,"text":"people still need to drink water."},{"time":58000,"text":"Most of the information that we collected on the cholera outbreak"},{"time":61000,"text":"didn't come from testing water;"},{"time":63000,"text":"it came from forms like this,"},{"time":65000,"text":"which documented all the people"},{"time":67000,"text":"we failed to help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69000,"text":"Countless lives have been saved"},{"time":71000,"text":"by canaries in coalmines --"},{"time":73000,"text":"a simple and invaluable way"},{"time":75000,"text":"for miners to know whether they're safe."},{"time":77000,"text":"I've been inspired by that simplicity as I've been working on this problem"},{"time":80000,"text":"with some of the most hardworking and brilliant people I've ever known."},{"time":83000,"text":"We think there's a simpler solution to this problem --"},{"time":85000,"text":"one that can be used"},{"time":87000,"text":"by people who face conditions like this everyday."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89000,"text":"It's in its early stages,"},{"time":91000,"text":"but this is what it looks like right now."},{"time":94000,"text":"We call it the Water Canary."},{"time":96000,"text":"It's a fast, cheap device"},{"time":99000,"text":"that answers an important question:"},{"time":101000,"text":"Is this water contaminated?"},{"time":103000,"text":"It doesn't require any special training."},{"time":106000,"text":"And instead of waiting for chemical reactions to take place,"},{"time":109000,"text":"it uses light."},{"time":111000,"text":"That means there's no waiting"},{"time":113000,"text":"for chemical reactions to take place,"},{"time":115000,"text":"no need to use reagents that can run out"},{"time":117000,"text":"and no need to be an expert"},{"time":119000,"text":"to get actionable information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122000,"text":"To test water, you simply insert a sample"},{"time":124000,"text":"and, within seconds,"},{"time":126000,"text":"it either displays a red light, indicating contaminated water,"},{"time":129000,"text":"or a green light, indicating the sample is safe."},{"time":131000,"text":"This will make it possible"},{"time":133000,"text":"for anyone to collect life-saving information"},{"time":136000,"text":"and to monitor water quality conditions as they unfold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139000,"text":"We're also, on top of that,"},{"time":142000,"text":"integrating wireless networking"},{"time":145000,"text":"into an affordable device"},{"time":147000,"text":"with GPS and GSM."},{"time":149000,"text":"What that means is that each reading can be automatically transmitted to servers"},{"time":152000,"text":"to be mapped in real time."},{"time":154000,"text":"With enough users,"},{"time":156000,"text":"maps like this will make it possible"},{"time":158000,"text":"to take preventive action,"},{"time":160000,"text":"containing hazards before they turn into emergencies"},{"time":163000,"text":"that take years to recover from."},{"time":165000,"text":"And then, instead of taking days"},{"time":167000,"text":"to disseminate this information to the people who need it most,"},{"time":169000,"text":"it can happen automatically."},{"time":172000,"text":"We've seen how distributed networks,"},{"time":174000,"text":"big data and information"},{"time":176000,"text":"can transform society."},{"time":178000,"text":"I think it's time for us to apply them to water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181000,"text":"Our goal over the next year is to get Water Canary ready for the field"},{"time":183000,"text":"and to open-source the hardware"},{"time":185000,"text":"so that anyone can contribute to the development and the evaluation,"},{"time":188000,"text":"so we can tackle this problem together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":190000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}